  "logNo": "110167825104",
  "title": "[추나요법한의원/체형교정한의원]허리디스크 치료방법 및 증상",
  "addDate": "2013. 5. 10.",
  "categoryNo": "13",
  "parentCategoryNo": "7",
  "url": "https://blog.naver.com/PostView.naver?blogId=isuhani&logNo=110167825104",
  "html_size": 190147,
  "body": "<div id=\"post-view110167825104\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea110167825104\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"font-size:9pt; font-family:'3028548_9';\" class=\"view\"><div style=\"font-size:9pt; font-family:'3028548_9';\" class=\"view\"> \r\n<div class=\"view\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '3028548_9'\">\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">[추나요법한의원/체형교정한의원]</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #1c4827\">허리디스크 치료방법 및 증상</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">어제 오후 부터 오늘 오전내내 비가 부슬부슬 내리네요 비가 오면 </p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">허리 통증이 더 하는 분들도 계시고 직장에 오래 앉아 계셔서 자고 일어나면 더 아픈분들도 계시지요?</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">원인은 여러가지 있겠지만 오늘은 허리디스크에 대해서 알아볼까 합니다</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/5b9f9f91e818a5c6.png\" width=\"550\" height=\"372\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 562px; rheight: 381px\" id=\"20130510_280/isuhani_1368152665233sNbmf_PNG/%C7%E3%B8%AE%B5%F0%BD%BA%C5%A91.PNG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6839AD0')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/5b9f9f91e818a5c6.png\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">흔히 ' 디스크 ' 라고 불리는 ' 척추추간판탈출증 ' 은 추간판(디스크)이 밀려나와서 신경을 압박하여 통증을 발생시키는 질환입니다</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #3a32c3\">(네모난 뼈 사이에 하얗게 보이는 타원모양이 정상디스크, 까맣게 변한게 디스크 퇴행, </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #3a32c3\">네모난 뼈 오른쪽 하얀 공간으로 까만게 비집고 나오는게 디스크 탈출)</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #3a32c3\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #3a32c3\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #3a32c3\"></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #3a32c3\"></span>&nbsp;<img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130510_297/isuhani_1368154230581kDE34_JPEG/B0ADB3B2C8F1_MRI1.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"470\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 550px; rheight: 470px\" id=\"20130510_297/isuhani_1368154230581kDE34_JPEG/B0ADB3B2C8F1_MRI1.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6839AD0')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130510_297/isuhani_1368154230581kDE34_JPEG/B0ADB3B2C8F1_MRI1.jpg?type=w3\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: '맑은 고딕'; language: en-US; mso-fareast-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt\"></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #3a32c3\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\">허리디스크(요추 추간판탈줄증)가 있는 경우 엉치, 다리로 이어지는 신경을 압박하므로 </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\">요통뿐 아니라 엉치와다리의 통증, 땡김, 저림, 마비, 무력감 등이 나타나기도 합니다</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\">갑자기 허리를 삐끗했는데, 꼼짝도 못하겠고 기침만 해도 허리가 울리듯 아프거나 </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\">다리가 저리는 경우엔 급성 허리디스크를 의심해봐야 하고, </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\">1~2주 정도 치료를 했는데도 증상이 완고하게 남았다면 검사를 받아 볼 필요가 있습니다</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\">평소 만성적인 요통과 함께 다리나 발의 저림, 당김 증상이 약하게 한번씩 느껴지곤 했었다면 더욱 주의를 기울여야 합니다</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/d69d049dc77a3a8d.png\" width=\"259\" height=\"253\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 259px; rheight: 253px\" id=\"20130510_155/isuhani_13681527030149RFDj_PNG/%C7%E3%B8%AE2.PNG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6839AD0')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/d69d049dc77a3a8d.png\"></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\">허리디스크 환자의 증상</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - 허리 엉치 다리 발이 당기고 저리는 통증이 있다</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - 허리 통증이 있다</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;- 재채기 기침 또는 배변시 통증이 심해진다</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - 누워서 쉬면 통증이 줄지만 활동을 하면 아파진다</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - 다리에 힘이 빠지는 느낌이 생기기도 한다</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"></span>&nbsp;<img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/2c583c8de2333fd9.png\" width=\"184\" height=\"304\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 184px; rheight: 304px\" id=\"20130510_48/isuhani_13681541556140VUHI_PNG/%C7%E3%B8%AE%B5%F0%BD%BA%C5%A92.PNG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6839AD0')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/2c583c8de2333fd9.png\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\">체형교정(추나요법) 이수한의원에서는 &nbsp;침치료와 더불어 봉침 또는 약침요법으로 디스크로 인한 염증과 통증을 다스리고, </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"></span><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"><u>추나요법으로 척추와 골반을 바르게 잡아주고, 척추 주변 근육의 균형을 맞춰주고</u>,</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><u><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\">&nbsp;한약으로 척추 디스크 주변의 인대와 근육을 강화해 줘야 </span><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\">근본적인 치료가 되고 재발을 막을 수 있습니다</span></u></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"><strong><span style=\"COLOR: #00b0a2\">&lt;추나요법한의원 진료시간안내&gt;</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/8cb3fe3c43069a09.png\" width=\"547\" height=\"172\" style=\"cursor: pointer;BORDER-LEFT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-BOTTOM-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-TOP-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-RIGHT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); rwidth: 547px; rheight: 172px\" id=\"20130510_272/isuhani_136815351106199T7C_PNG/%C7%D1%C0%C7%BF%F8%C1%F8%B7%E1%BD%C3%B0%A3%C7%A52.PNG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6839AD0')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/8cb3fe3c43069a09.png\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/1f95d77c9398142d.png\" width=\"266\" height=\"66\" style=\"cursor: pointer;BORDER-LEFT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-BOTTOM-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-TOP-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-RIGHT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); rwidth: 266px; rheight: 66px\" id=\"20130510_218/isuhani_1368153512445s5Rpc_PNG/2013-03-18_14%3B49%3B33.PNG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6839AD0')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/1f95d77c9398142d.png\"></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #3a32c3\"></span>&nbsp;</p></div></div></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
